meeseepics (1.0.5) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add option to change sort order of file list.
  * Add option to show/hide hidden directories and files.
  * Remember slide-show settings.
  * Increase size of navigation border.

 -- Sebastian Sauer <sebastian.sauer@kdab.com>  Thu, 01 Aug 2012 20:25:42 +0200

meeseepics (1.0.4) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add slide-show mode.
  * Add option to switch between light or dark theme.
  * Add option to display more detailed infos for image files.
  * Add option to change size of thumbnails.

 -- Sebastian Sauer <sebastian.sauer@kdab.com>  Thu, 26 Jun 2012 20:25:42 +0200

meeseepics (1.0.3) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fix cases where switching between zoom-to-fit and double-zoom did not work as expected.
  * Improve directory items so it's more easy to click them.
  * Optimize changing directories.
  * Optimize load thumbnail from ~/.thumbnails/grid/md5(pathQUrl).jpeg when exists.
  * Optimize load thumbnail from exif if an image embeds a thumbnail in it's exif.
  * Optimize image vs thumbnail loading by using different threadPool's for them.

 -- Sebastian Sauer <sebastian.sauer@kdab.com>  Sun, 20 May 2012 20:25:42 +0200

